Notes:
Socket Types :
<> Stream Sockets : Connection oriented & sequenced; tcp, sctp, bluetooth; User space
<> Datagram Sockets : Connectionless; udp; User Space
<> Raw Sockets : Direct sending & recieving w/o automatic protocol specific formatting; Kernel Space

Network Programming w/Python3:
<> import socket
<><> s = socket.socket(socket.FAMILY, socket.TYPE, socket.PROTOCOL)
<><> family should be : AF_INET or AF_INET6 or AF_UNIX
<><> type should be : SOCK_STREAM or SOCK_DGRAM or SOCK_RAW
<><> proto should be : 0 or IPPROTO_RAW
